# ===========================================
# SECURITY NOTES:
#
# 1. NEVER commit files containing:
#    - API keys or tokens
#    - Investigation results with PII
#    - Database files with sensitive data
#    - Screenshots or evidence files
#
# 2. Before pushing to public repos:
#    - Review all committed files
#    - Ensure no sensitive data is included
#    - Test with dummy data only
#
# 3. If you accidentally commit sensitive data:
#    - Remove it immediately
#    - Rewrite history if necessary
